                          "String": "/SIGNS AND SYMPTOMS/ Most important effect of pentachlorophenol inhalation is acute poisoning centering in circulatory system with accompanying heart failure ... Dusts are particularly irritating to eyes and nose in concn greater than 1 mg/cu m. Some irritation of nose may occur at 0.3 mg/cu m ... Survivors of ... intoxication suffer ... visual damage and acute type of scotoma. Other damage incl acute inflammation of conjunctiva and characteristically shaped corneal opacity, corneal numbness, and slight mydriasis.",
